---
title: Carb Smart Halloumi and Tabbouleh Bowls with Creamy Sesame Sauce
description: Golden, squeaky cheese? Yes please! With halloumi sitting pretty on top of whole grain bulgur with tender veggies and a super sauce, this dinner has it all.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

